{"tid":38341,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"30秒狂出221拳9歲妹赤手打穿房門","createTime":"2016-12-14T00:46:21.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-14T14:08:13.000Z","uid":63669,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a3f35a28c2c1f1de4d63618543cc0893e7bd75a5","tid":38341,"uid":63669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T00:46:21.000Z","msg":"小孩子發脾氣非同小可，隨時亂扔東西或故意塗花牆壁等，然而哈薩克這名9歲小女孩更加惹不得，因為熱愛拳擊的她雖年紀輕輕，拳速及拳重已不可小覷，更赤手空拳打穿過自己的睡房門。<br />\n<br />\n9歲女孩薩德瓦卡索夫（Evnika Sadvakasov）被譽為「拳擊神童」，小小手臂有著結實的肌肉，在教練父親魯斯塔姆（Rustam）的訓練下，上月曾在俄羅斯一個電視節目中，表演在30秒內打出221拳的驚人紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n父親日前上載女兒在房內練拳的短片，可見她在一輪快拳熱身後，不斷狂轟睡房門，結果轟出一個大洞。雖然雙手都打到發紅，但她似乎一點也不覺得痛，再慢慢收拾被她打到掉下的地球儀、拳套等雜物。<br />\n<br />\n魯斯塔姆表示：「自從我們允許女兒可以破壞房間內任何東西，及赤手空拳打穿大門後，她在學校的表現明顯有進步。」他指家中早有規例，容許孩子在牆壁上塗鴉或做任何事，但只限空手，不能使用任何工具。<br />\n<br />\n他坦言女兒可以赤手空拳打穿房門，令他也相當驚訝，而隨著女兒一直長大，出拳力道也越來越大。他說笑稱：「如果你想測試門的強度，可以找薩德瓦卡索夫！」<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日鏡報》"},{"pid":"598413f9f8ee64e95917f235ab33b0bf76adb68e","tid":38341,"uid":33234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T00:47:30.000Z","msg":"修道船<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a3ebe6bc3ac8fdd2aaa86f2bc906f3045fdbeda","tid":38341,"uid":61494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T00:49:12.000Z","msg":"修道船再世<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80cb7cf95223f7e23ca7568d75f25da862e80998","tid":38341,"uid":61864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T00:49:18.000Z","msg":"留名不留情"},{"pid":"9babaae4718d3554b6d119a71d3a17df3b47a4e9","tid":38341,"uid":33483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T00:53:22.000Z","msg":"三十秒得個二百幾拳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0137e652b0bb699f081ced5667de089cf9110d70","tid":38341,"uid":48942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T00:56:32.000Z","msg":"唔否認佢拳速同拳重係幾勁<br />\n但今次好明顯係房門虧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce5c6cf5446dfcdacc5000e7a0dfbfcc5c573bb5","tid":38341,"uid":60655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T00:58:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>修道船再世<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n9秒100拳 同30秒221拳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce47d059d690c935d3babbf2068d2fe49c2cd0e3","tid":38341,"uid":47966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T01:01:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>修道船再世<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n9秒100拳 同30秒221拳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n修道船<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 完"},{"pid":"b9c6fd8d70b1cb4bc6f1ab533dfe6296f72029fe","tid":38341,"uid":8776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T01:39:43.000Z","msg":"星矢個女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"515026d3de613019c2b09c899275b4be180c9612","tid":38341,"uid":22574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T01:44:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">オラオラオラオラオラオラ</span>"},{"pid":"25aba06d17d38b997d60bb7dd5b878142b1a44bc","tid":38341,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T02:04:07.000Z","msg":"係咪假新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 片呢"},{"pid":"cc144743fd0b75563e1508f6a680572d8c08badd","tid":38341,"uid":36544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T03