al/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n葉問 有冇佢咁快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3103c4d34102c7418dd326852327117124d78edf","tid":38341,"uid":57303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T10:27:01.000Z","msg":"我諗真正有效既應該係200拳以下<br />\n因為一開頭佢有d拳冇伸直所以好快收拳"},{"pid":"1304c74b9ac40fa8a4ff9cf6b284edb768f1cd87","tid":38341,"uid":22553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T10:30:10.000Z","msg":"試下實木門先講啦"},{"pid":"9dff9093b948cdcc8a090f42aff64c4d14e43c7b","tid":38341,"uid":14598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T10:32:58.000Z","msg":"後面明顯痛爆"},{"pid":"f66e9554a28ba488ac53e612f0befeadbb332e30","tid":38341,"uid":39698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T10:34:35.000Z","msg":"打丁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87e704479ed9e2cbf6dd4b2df93c6f3479c47c08","tid":38341,"uid":4286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T11:19:02.000Z","msg":"Vivid<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2db5975fb4db5499d49086e4699cb4d2b50086e5","tid":38341,"uid":42452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T12:12:43.000Z","msg":"修道船: 9秒100拳<br />\n俄羅斯女神童: 30秒221拳<br />\n<br />\n問: 女神童在9秒內能打出多少拳<br />\n<br />\n答:<br />\n9/30 x 221 = 67拳 (原為66.3拳, 故取整數)<br />\n因為修道船能在9秒內打出100拳    <br />\n所以, 100-67=33<br />\n<br />\n因此, 俄羅斯女神童在9秒戰內敗給修道船33拳"},{"pid":"e6f6f25fdf7169e332ee225ad2011227042e60c2","tid":38341,"uid":42527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T12:21:56.000Z","msg":"我想知佢點唔用工具而塗鴉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e07cc8841f2766c8fd17633dc684bdc478a4cd3","tid":38341,"uid":50598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":